OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,FKatie Oscroft hears from friends of
OL,7,FChris Marriott
OL,9,FWhen Chris Marriott saw a stranger
OL,10,Flying prone in the road during a
OL,11,Ffamily walk, his instinct to stop and
OL,12,Fhelp was, friends say, typical.
OL,14,F"It was who he was," Natalie Williams
OL,15,Fsays.
OL,17,F"He was a good Samaritan actually,
OL,18,Fthat's how he lived his life."
