OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,FMr Marriott was with his wife and two
OL,7,Fyoung sons when he saw a woman injured
OL,8,Fon the ground on College Court in
OL,9,FBurngreave, Sheffield, on 27 December
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FAs he tended to her, midwife Alison
OL,13,FNorris also stopped to help.
OL,15,FShe said: "I don't think it's anything
OL,16,Fspecial. I know a lot of people would
OL,17,Fhave done the same thing.
OL,19,F"I honestly think, certainly round our
OL,20,Fway, that's what people do."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
