OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,FTheir simple act of charity, however,
OL,7,Fwould end up costing both of them
OL,8,Fdearly.
OL,10,FLittle did they know that they had
OL,11,Fstumbled upon a violent family feud
OL,12,Fand into the path of an angry driver.
OL,14,FMs Norris said: "Before I'd had a
OL,15,Fchance to properly assess, a car came
OL,16,Fat us.
OL,18,F"It was so quick, it was even too
OL,19,Fquick to be frightened. I just had to
OL,20,Ftry and move. I don't even really know
OL,21,Fhow I moved, but I did."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
