OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,FMoments after they stopped to help,
OL,7,Fboth Mr Marriott and Ms Norris were
OL,8,Fhit by a car.
OL,10,FMs Norris suffered serious injuries.
OL,11,FFour others were also injured and
OL,12,Fsurvived. Mr Marriott died at the
OL,13,Fscene.
OL,15,FThe car was being driven by Hassan
OL,16,FJhangur. His sister, Amaani, had got
OL,17,Fmarried earlier that day to Hasan Khan.
