OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,FA feud between the couple's families
OL,7,Ferupted into a brawl when the bride's
OL,8,Fmother, Ambreen, and sister, Nafeesa,
OL,9,Farrived outside the Khan family home
OL,10,Fon College Close.
OL,12,FNafeesa Khan was the woman Mr Marriott
OL,13,Fand Ms Norris were trying to help when
OL,14,FHassan Jhangur ploughed into them.
OL,16,FIn the course of the collision Jhangur
OL,17,Falso injured his own mother and
OL,18,Fsister, along with the groom's father,
OL,19,FRiasat Khan.
