OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,FHe then got out of the car and stabbed
OL,7,Fhis new brother-in-law Hasan Khan.
OL,9,FIt was perhaps a miracle that no-one
OL,10,Felse died.
OL,12,FIn the aftermath of Mr Marriott's
OL,13,Fdeath, his family described him as "a
OL,14,Fwonderful husband, dad, brother, uncle
OL,15,F` and friend to many."
OL,17,F"The circumstances of his death,
OL,18,Falthough tragic and unfathomable to
OL,19,Fus, his family, show the sort of man
OL,20,Fhe was ` to go to help rather than to
OL,21,Fturn away," they said.
