OL,3,CThe man whose 'gift' for helping
OL,4,Cothers cost him his life
OL,6,F"Chris was also a man of faith who
OL,7,Fwanted others to also experience the
OL,8,Fjoy he had found trusting in Jesus."
OL,10,FFriend Ben Gibbins, who had known
OL,11,FChris Marriott for several years, said
OL,12,Fhe had a "gift to affect people's
OL,13,Flives".
OL,15,F"It still feels unreal," he said. "It
OL,16,Fstill feels like a huge loss... there
OL,17,Fis a big hole missing."
