OL,6,FJhangur now faces a life sentence for
OL,7,Fthe murder of Chris Marriott. For Mr
OL,8,FMarriott's loved ones, the sense of
OL,9,Ffutility
OL,11,FAlison Norris says there was "no need"
OL,12,Ffor what happened, "no rational reason
OL,13,Ffor it".
OL,15,F"If there's one thing that is a legacy
OL,16,Fto him (it) is to stop and think and
OL,17,Fnot act destructively."
